{"tid":1944262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱示威者為「曱甴」的梁偉雄將於 4 月 18 日出任消防處處長","createTime":"2020-03-26T09:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:21:08.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebb7e9824e5b4b6b32ea8e23887d32c03ec1a47","tid":1944262,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"政府今日（26 日）下午宣布，現任消防處副處長梁偉雄，將於 4 月 18 日出任消防處處長，接替於同日展開退休前休假的李建日。梁偉雄過往曾經發表爭議言論，包括去年在反送中運動期間，曾經在內部講座稱示威者為「曱甴」，引起部分消防處職員不滿&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n梁偉雄在去年曾經發表爭議言論：10 月 29 日，梁在消防及救護學院出席一個約 100 人參與的講座，講座內容是涉及消防處人員面對公眾活動時的做法。梁偉雄發言期間，曾經指示威者是「曱甴」，他們的行為是「殺人」，提醒同事小心，「因為街有好多曱甴唔安全，你影佢哋，佢哋會打你」。梁偉雄又表示支持警察，指他們「都好辛苦」，要靠他們「維持法治」，並且說公務員要「政治中立」意指效忠政府和特首。<br />\n<br />\n消防處其後證實，梁偉雄曾用「曱甴」來形容「這些罔顧法紀的暴徒」，而該講座屬於內部交流，內容不對外公開。當時有消防處人員形容，不論消防和救護人員均對梁偉雄的說話十分反感，他指示威者是「曱甴」明顯違反政治中立和救急扶危的精神，擔心影響消防處聲譽，以及市民對消防處執行職務的信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7-%E6%A2%81%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258E%25A5%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259B%2584%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=94187c90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258E%25A5%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259B%2584%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%2F&h=03e129a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7-%E6%A2%81%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4/</a>"},{"pid":"73f98d32b23bf2cc50a40db7f90a4f670bf7b3d8","tid":1944262,"uid":15823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"高職位, 肯奶就有"},{"pid":"2bd47ff0e39207bb09992498b6e2121a8d4969dc","tid":1944262,"uid":58209,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"姓梁無一個係好人<br />\n梁振英 梁愛詩 梁家輝 <br />\n<br />\n利申：姓梁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25476d86db0ec66597f6219f6849a827510f3458","tid":1944262,"uid":103981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2bd47ff0e39207bb09992498b6e2121a8d4969dc","tid":1944262,"uid":58209,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"姓梁無一個係好人<br />\n梁振英 梁愛詩 梁家輝 <br />\n<br />\n利申：姓梁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"梁天琦？"},{"pid":"12089056a7370acd240e86b67117a18fe01a6897","tid":1944262,"uid":56432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"真！！！！<br />\n跟親姓梁嘅老細，男男女女都仆街都震<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb681e035968159309a9e7244909e2e80319afc9","tid":1944262,"uid":189328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"佢做唔做處長都無分別,消防員比黑警打班細都唔企出黎<b